      <para>
        <!--both <application>
Python 2</application> and -->
Pour construire le module <application>Python 3</application>, lancez&nbsp;:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        To install the module, issue the following command as the &root; user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir lxml</userinput></screen>

